reviewText: Five Stars all the way, Jenna Kim Jones is hilarious and embracing new media by doing it on her own her self. She can also be heard regularly on Alison Rosen podcast, Alison Rosen is Your New Best Friend. She is a young clean, Mormon comedian, everyone should check her out and support a young up and coming comedian.
She is the best!! First rating! I am so happy! Everyone get it! Its the best. Super funny for sure.

There is something interestingly conversational about this. I felt like I had a funny BFF sitting in my family room making me laugh. It was friendly and funny and I liked it. Even my husband who can be somewhat a grump about stand up enjoyed it.
Hilarious. Beautiful. And refreshingly clean.
Thank you Jenna Kim Jones for a hilarious video and I look forward to listening to you every Thursday on Alison Rosen is your new  best friend!
Funny stand up special, family friendly too! I recommend it to friends and family. #JKJ4AFV
